summary: A lazy Racemenu preset i made after a night of drinks
descriptionHtml:
Ever wanted to hate eggplants, slay dogslime, devour pudding souls, and get shouted at by a sentient book as the Dragonborn? Well now you can!

Disclaimer: If you actually want that to happen, you'd have to make a mod yourself. This is just a Racemenu Preset and nothing more.

Equip with Tachis or two handed Katanas from any mod, and use the Nephilim mod and Athletics mod with 200 speed and high jump settings for a full immersive experience as full as this run-on sentence my old grade school teacher would cry at.

Install this manually in your [Skyrim > Data > SKSE > Plugins > CharGen > Presets] folder, if SKSE and onwards do not exist, run the game and try looking again or create the folders yourself.

Hard Requirements:

Apachii Sky Hair - Apachii
CBBE - Caliente
Eyes of Beauty - LogRaam
Live Another Life Alternate Start - Arthmoor
Skyrim - Bethesda
Pretty Face - tktk1

Suggested (But not Needed):

Nephilim - Jetsteele
Athletics Training - Volek
author: Pudding04
